summary:
I am a proactive person with more than 10 years of experience working. Managing crisis and problem solving are key aspects that I learnt to manage while working in the government.
I enjoy environments where I can interact with new people and develop networks, always useful to achieve better results. Challenges make me work in a more active and passionate way. 
Currently: starting the adventure of becoming a PhD. 
In my free time: travel, running, my source of creativity and tennis from time to time.
